make for a fantastic special occasion dinner. And to really make jaws drop, we’ll whip up a fruity pineapple cheesecake with a
coconut caramel sauce for dessert. Dig in!

*To download the recipe card for the main and dessert, click the download arrow on the right of the screen.*

